<br>
Quit crying about people who don't know how to control aggro.  It's their problem not yours.  If it's really as bad as people claim it is there isn't anything you can do about it anyway.  You're not going to get any improvement from SoE.  Anything short of making AE taunt refresh in 6 seconds and taunt work as enraging blow still won't make you more desirable than a Knight, and the way to fix the game isn't to break it even more.  If they made warrior aggro +200% Knights will still be more desirable for aggro because they can do it at range and don't have to rely on procs.  Whining about improving warriors isn't going to help anything, and even if SoE listen, it's still probably not going to do anything given how broken Knights are.  The solution is to nerf Knights and anything else would either not work at all or completely break the game.   <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=468916">Phantron</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=phantron>Phantron</A> at: 1/21/03 2:26:21 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=frodlin7th>Frodlin7th</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 267<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/21/03 2:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1800.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: No, there isn't any aggro control problem.</span><hr size=1> Phantron,<br>
